dc_title_s: Carte geologique detaillee de la France [a 1/80 000]: Chatellerault
dc_description_s: France. Bureau de recherches geologiques et minieres [BRGM]. Carte geologique 1:80.000 CG-132(1952) France. Service de la carte geologique de France North Decimal Degree 46.9729 South Decimal Degree 46.6131 East Decimal Degree 1.0752 West Decimal Degree 0.2342 Relief shown by hachures. Principal meridian: Paris. Longitude is given in centesimal values (100 grades = 90 degrees) .The Service de la carte geologique de la France was integrated to the BRGM to become the only France Service geologique national. Based on "Carte topograqphique de l'etat major."
